public static SymbolicPolynomial getConditionForEqualsConvexAngles()

Returns:

getConditionForSupplementaryConvexAngles

public static SymbolicPolynomial getConditionForSupplementaryConvexAngles()
Method that gives the condition for supplementary convex angles (whose sum is pi). These angles are of same orientation. If angles are of opposite orientation then this method gives the condition for them to be equals (as plain geometric angles).

Returns:
Symbolic polynomial representing the condition
